# End-to-end expectation for stage 1 (attack surface) on mqtt-mini-client.
# After a successful `run.sh stage1 <repo>`, concatenate all runs/.../AS/AS*.md (excluding
# _raw.md); every non-comment, non-empty line below must match that blob at least once
# (grep -E -q). Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# Ground truth for what the model should surface: ../mqtt-mini-client/VULNS.md

# Primary implementation file
mqtt_client\.cpp

# Hostname / argv overflow surface (VULNS §1)
(strcpy|parse_args_pub|parse_args_sub)

# Inbound PUBLISH topic handling (VULNS §2)
(unsafe_copy_topic|topic_buf|topic_len)

# Debug peek past topic (VULNS §3)
debug_peek_past_topic

# Remaining-length / framing accumulation (VULNS §4)
read_remaining_length
